<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<%- include('../partials/funil-meta', {
  ogTitle: 'Lista de espera | AIRPET',
  metaDescription: 'Lista de espera AIRPET: poucas perguntas, tom de conversa — sorteio de AirTag (30 por cidade, sem pagar nada) e data do sorteio no WhatsApp.',
  ogDescription: 'Entra na lista em poucos minutos. Sorteio de AirTag por cidade; a data avisamos no WhatsApp.',
  ogUrl: (typeof BASE_URL !== 'undefined' ? BASE_URL : '') + '/lista-espera',
  ogImage: (typeof BASE_URL !== 'undefined' ? BASE_URL : '') + '/images/landing/og.jpg',
  canonicalUrl: (typeof BASE_URL !== 'undefined' ? BASE_URL : '') + '/lista-espera',
  jsonLd: null,
  themeColor: '#fafaf7',
}) %>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
</head>
<body class="le-wizard-page antialiased" id="lista-espera-body">
<%- include('../partials/funil-header', { funilHeaderDark: false, funilBackHref: '/proteger-meu-pet' }) %>

<div class="le-progress-wrap" aria-hidden="false">
  <div class="le-progress-inner">
    <div class="le-progress-top">
      <span id="leProgressLabel">Passo 1 de 6 — Seus dados</span>
      <span id="leProgressPct">17%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="le-progress-bar-outer" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="1" aria-valuemax="6" aria-valuenow="1" aria-labelledby="leProgressLabel" id="leProgressBarWrap">
      <div id="leProgressBar" class="le-progress-bar-inner" style="width:17%"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<main id="conteudo-principal" class="le-main">
  <p id="leLiveRegion" class="sr-only" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"></p>
  <div id="listaEsperaWizard" class="relative overflow-hidden" data-autoadvance="true" data-referral="<%= typeof referralOrigem !== 'undefined' && referralOrigem ? String(referralOrigem).replace(/"/g, '') : '' %>">

    <section class="le-step" data-step="1" data-step-label="Seus dados">
      <h1>Antes de tudo: como a gente te chama?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead">A gente não enche caixa de spam. Quem termina o passo a passo entra no <strong>sorteio de AirTag</strong> — <strong>30 tutores por cidade</strong>, sem pagar nada. A <strong>data do sorteio</strong> e as novidades mandamos no <strong>WhatsApp</strong> no número que você deixar aqui.</p>
      <div class="le-field">
        <label for="leNome">Seu nome <span class="text-red-600" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="leNome" name="nome" maxlength="120" autocomplete="name" placeholder="Ex.: Marina Silva" required>
      </div>
      <div class="le-field">
        <label for="leEmail">E-mail <span class="text-red-600" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <input type="email" id="leEmail" name="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" required>
      </div>
      <p id="errStep1" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <button type="button" class="le-next lp-btn-primary w-full justify-center">Continuar</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="le-step hidden" data-step="2" data-step-label="Seu pet">
      <h1>Quem é o astro da casa?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead mt-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Qual é o seu pet <span class="text-red-600">*</span></p>
      <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2" data-single="tipo_pet" role="group" aria-label="Qual é o seu pet">
        <button type="button" class="le-pet-card flex flex-col items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="cachorro" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">🐶</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">Cachorro</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-pet-card flex flex-col items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="gato" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">🐱</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">Gato</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-pet-card flex flex-col items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="outro" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">🐾</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">Outro</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Quantos moram na sua rotina? <span class="text-red-600">*</span></p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2" data-single="qtd_pets" role="group" aria-label="Quantos pets moram com você">
        <button type="button" class="le-chip rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700" data-value="1" aria-pressed="false">1</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-chip rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700" data-value="2" aria-pressed="false">2</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-chip rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700" data-value="3+" aria-pressed="false">3 ou mais</button>
      </div>
      <p id="errStep2" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <button type="button" class="le-next lp-btn-primary flex-1 justify-center">Continuar</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-prev rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3.5 px-6">Voltar</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="le-step hidden" data-step="3" data-step-label="Experiência">
      <h1>Já passou por um sumiço ou susto do tamanho do mundo?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead">Conta com sinceridade — aqui não tem resposta errada, só história de verdade.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-3" data-single="ja_perdeu_pet" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Se você já passou por sumiço ou susto com pet">
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 flex gap-4 items-start hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="sim" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Sim, já perdi um pet</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 flex gap-4 items-start hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="quase" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M12 20a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Quase perdi, foi por pouco</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 flex gap-4 items-start hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="nao" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Nunca perdi, mas tenho medo</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <p id="errStep3" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <button type="button" class="le-next lp-btn-primary flex-1 justify-center">Continuar</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-prev rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3.5 px-6">Voltar</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="le-step hidden" data-step="4" data-step-label="Primeiros passos">
      <h1>Se sumisse agora, o que você faria primeiro?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead">Marca tudo que faria de verdade — não o que “deveria” no papel.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-2" data-multi="metodos_busca" role="group" aria-label="O que você faria na prática se o pet sumisse agora">
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="whatsapp">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 18h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Grupos de WhatsApp do bairro</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="facebook">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 4v16M17 4v16M3 8h4m10 0h4M3 12h18M3 16h4m10 0h4"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Facebook / Instagram</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="panfletos">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6M5 4h14l-1 16H6L5 4z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Panfletos na rua</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="rua">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Sair andando e procurar</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="veterinario">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4.5 9.5l7.5-5 7.5 5M4.5 9.5V19h15V9.5"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Ligar para clínicas e abrigos</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="outro">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Não saberia o que fazer</span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <p id="errStep4" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <button type="button" class="le-next lp-btn-primary flex-1 justify-center">Continuar</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-prev rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3.5 px-6">Voltar</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="le-step hidden" data-step="5" data-step-label="O que importa">
      <h1>O que mais ajudaria você no pior momento?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead">Escolhe até duas opções — ajuda a gente a saber o que mais importa pra você na hora H.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-2" data-multi="prioridades" data-max="2" role="group" aria-label="O que mais importa pra você nessa hora">
        <label class="le-check le-prio flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="identificar_dono">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Saber na hora de quem é o pet</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check le-prio flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="contato_tutor">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Falar com o dono em segundos</span>
        </label>
        <label class="le-check le-prio flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 cursor-pointer hover:border-primary-200 has-[:checked]:border-primary-500 has-[:checked]:bg-orange-50/60">
          <input type="checkbox" class="le-check-input sr-only" value="ultima_localizacao">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Ver por onde o pet passou</span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <p id="errStep5" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <button type="button" class="le-next lp-btn-primary flex-1 justify-center">Continuar</button>
        <button type="button" class="le-prev rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3.5 px-6">Voltar</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="le-step hidden" data-step="6" data-step-label="Cidade e contato">
      <h1>Último passo: onde você está nessa história?</h1>
      <p class="le-lead">Cidade e contato ajudam a gente a ver onde tem mais gente esperando e a te avisar quando a vez chegar na sua região.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
        <div class="col-span-2 le-field mt-0">
          <label for="leCidade">Cidade</label>
          <input type="text" id="leCidade" maxlength="80" placeholder="Sua cidade" autocomplete="address-level2">
        </div>
        <div class="le-field mt-0">
          <label for="leEstado">UF</label>
          <input type="text" id="leEstado" maxlength="2" placeholder="SP" autocomplete="address-level1" class="uppercase">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="le-field">
        <label for="leTelefone">WhatsApp / celular (recomendado)</label>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-2">A gente usa pra avisar a <strong>data do sorteio da AirTag</strong> e quando tiver novidade de verdade na sua região — sem encher seu saco.</p>
        <input type="tel" id="leTelefone" maxlength="30" placeholder="(00) 00000-0000" autocomplete="tel">
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Quando abrir por aí, quer ser dos primeiros a saber? <span class="text-red-600">*</span></p>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-2" data-single="beta_interesse" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Quer ser avisado cedo quando chegar na sua região">
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 flex gap-3 items-center hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="sim" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Sim, quero ser dos primeiros</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 flex gap-3 items-center hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="talvez" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Talvez, depende</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-big-card w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 flex gap-3 items-center hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors" data-value="nao" aria-pressed="false">
          <svg class="le-icon-inline shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Ainda não, mas quero acompanhar</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <input type="text" id="leWebsite" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" class="absolute opacity-0 pointer-events-none h-0 w-0" aria-hidden="true">
      <p id="errStep6" class="mt-3 text-sm text-red-600 hidden" role="alert"></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <button type="button" id="leSubmit" class="lp-btn-primary w-full justify-center disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed flex items-center gap-2">
          <span id="leSubmitLabel">Enviar minha inscrição</span>
          <svg id="leSubmitSpinner" class="hidden w-5 h-5 animate-spin" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle>
            <path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4z"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="le-prev rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3">Voltar</button>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400 text-center">
        <a href="/privacidade?funil=1" class="underline hover:text-primary-600">Política de privacidade</a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/funil-footer') %>
<script src="/js/funil-analytics.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/lista-espera-wizard.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
